                <p><img src="http://www.accidentsolutionllc.com/images/cfc54090c391466ae65631e82156c58f14643b41.jpg" style="width: 743px;" class="fr-dib" loading="lazy"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 26px;"><strong>Know Your Rights</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 26px;"><strong>Our Service is FREE and Here to Help You.</strong></span><br><br></p><p id="isPasted"><span style="font-size: 16px;">If you&rsquo;ve been involved in an auto accident, you may be feeling overwhelmed and alone, not knowing how to navigate the process of finding the right attorney to assist you with your individual case. And time is of the essence. Accident Solution is here to help. We are a FREE directory designed to help accident victims quickly and easily find help from qualified legal providers.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;">When you search for an attorney on Accident Solution, you&rsquo;ll find experienced, qualified professionals who match your needs in the areas where you need help. We verify the professionals&rsquo; licenses and ensure that they are accepting new clients on a contingency basis, where applicable, so that you can be confident that you are in good hands should you choose them to help you.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Our consumers also rate their personal experiences with the providers they select to help us maintain confidence that the attorneys on our directory are providing the best service.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Once you choose a category, you will have the option to review a number of provider profiles prior to making a selection. This allows you to select an attorney that most closely matches your needs. You will then be able to immediately contact your chosen provider via telephone, email, or text message to arrange a free consultation.</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#" rel="noopener noreferrer" ta